@startuml PocketPD State Machine

skinparam backgroundColor #1a1a2e
skinparam state {
    BackgroundColor #16213e
    BorderColor #00d4ff
    FontColor #e0e0e0
    ArrowColor #888888
}
skinparam note {
    BackgroundColor #0a0a1a
    BorderColor #444444
    FontColor #aaaaaa
}

title PocketPD State Machine

state BOOT : Show splash screen\n(500ms)
state OBTAIN : Read PDOs from\nUSB PD charger
state CAPDISPLAY : Show available\npower profiles\n(3s timeout)

state "Normal Operation" as normal {
    state NORMAL_PPS : PPS mode\nFine V/I control\n(20mV / 50mA steps)
    state NORMAL_PDO : Fixed PDO mode\nPre-set voltage profiles

    state choice <<choice>>
    choice --> NORMAL_PPS : has PPS
    choice --> NORMAL_PDO : fixed only
}

state MENU : Profile selection\nEncoder navigates\nlist

[*] --> BOOT

BOOT --> OBTAIN : 500ms elapsed

OBTAIN --> CAPDISPLAY : PDOs parsed

CAPDISPLAY --> choice : 3s timeout\nor any button

CAPDISPLAY --> choice : any button press

NORMAL_PPS --> MENU : encoder\nlong press
NORMAL_PDO --> MENU : encoder\nlong press

MENU --> choice : select\nlong press\n(apply profile)

note right of NORMAL_PPS
  **Encoder rotation**: adjust target V or I
  **Encoder short**: cycle step scale
  **Select short**: toggle V/I adjust
  **Output short**: toggle output on/off
  **Output long**: toggle energy display
end note

note left of MENU
  **Encoder rotation**: navigate profiles
  **Select long**: confirm & return
end note

@enduml
